00:42:24.238 --> 00:42:25.518
Sure Ellis will
take care of her.

779
00:42:27.937 --> 00:42:29.982
Um. I've been meaning
to say thank you

780
00:42:30.113 --> 00:42:31.248
for what you did
the other night.

781
00:42:31.332 --> 00:42:32.550
Oh. yeah.
Absolutely.

782
00:42:32.681 --> 00:42:34.164
