00:43:20.250 --> 00:43:21.512
Sheriff. can I. um...

801
00:43:21.643 --> 00:43:23.862
Hey. would you guys
excuse me for a second?

802
00:43:23.993 --> 00:43:25.606
I just need to have
a word with my deputy.

803
00:43:25.690 --> 00:43:26.690
Of course.

804
00:43:27.997 --> 00:43:31.566
