We're gonna
figure it out together.

822
00:44:31.713 --> 00:44:32.717
<i>♪ Everybody's saying that ♪</i>

823
00:44:32.801 --> 00:44:34.368
Don't worry.

824
00:44:34.498 --> 00:44:36.239
<i>♪ Hell's the hippest
