Hey. hey!

841
00:45:43.828 --> 00:45:45.221
Oh! Oh. no. no. no.
Okay. here!

842
00:45:45.351 --> 00:45:48.564
Grab her... grab her arm.
grab her arm! Hold on. hold on!

843
00:45:50.879 --> 00:45:55.710
